    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Color Game</strong>. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you play our game.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect any personal information from users directly. However, the Game may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> This includes details such as device type, operating system, and IP address.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use the Game, including gameplay statistics, preferences, or error reports.</li>
      <li><strong>Third-Party Services:</strong> The Game may integrate services such as Google Play Services, which may collect personal data like your IP address, device information, or location for analytics and advertising purposes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect information used to identify you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Play Services Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Unity Ads Privacy Policy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Improve Game Experience:</strong> To enhance your experience, personalise content, or resolve issues.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising and Analytics:</strong> To support revenue generation and game improvements using cookies and tracking technologies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal data with third parties, except as required by law or as necessary to support the services above.</p>

    <h2>5. Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your data. However, no method of internet transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may access, amend, or delete your personal data via the privacy settings of third-party services like Google Play or Unity, as we do not collect data directly.</p>

    <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>This Game is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us and we will delete it.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Updates will be noted in the Game and on this page. Please review it regularly for any changes.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy, feel free to reach out:</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:sedgesltd@gmail.com">sedgesltd@gmail.com</a></p>

